y components argues against the swallowing of a\nmassive planet by one of the stars after the convective zones have shrunk to\ntheir present-day sizes.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 2 May 2018 17:50:33 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-08-08"}
