uments. Our approach will also benefit other H\\,{\\sc i} intensity mapping\nexperiments that face similar challenges, such as those measuring Baryon\nAcoustic Oscillations (BAO).\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 2 May 2018 18:01:28 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-07-04"}
