ence of the wake-mode in 3D rectangular cavity flows is due to the release\nof kinetic energy from the spanwise vortices to the streamwise vortical\nstructures that develops from the spanwise instabilities.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 2 May 2018 21:48:33 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-05-04"}
