ed active scheme and ensemble based passive schemes. The\nexperimental results show that the proposed active scheme based ensemble\nlearning algorithm significantly enhances the BCI performance in MI\nclassifications.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 2 May 2018 22:21:38 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-05-04"}
