y between the range of 67% and 83%, and thus\nillustrates the feasibility of leveraging machine learning and\nfluorescence-based spectral-morphological features as a viable method for\nautomated identification of different algae types.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 3 May 2018 03:07:37 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-05-04"}
