\nmay be useful for scaled EOT devices but does not lead to sub-60 mV/dec SS.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 3 May 2018 07:41:33 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 6 May 2018 19:38:52 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 26 Jul 2018 02:54:09 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-07-27"}
