r example, for the mass of 1.7 Msun the\nequatorial radius is Req = 11.9+0.5 -0.4 km. Finally, we show that further\nimprovements can be obtained when the X-ray polarization data from the Imaging\nX-ray Polarimeter Explorer will become available.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 3 May 2018 07:47:32 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 29 Oct 2018 07:01:13 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-10-31"}
