e\nshown that this process can be a major source of O($^3$P), O($^1$D), O($^1$S),\nC($^3$P) and C($^1$D) produced in the cometary coma at small cometocentric\ndistances.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 3 May 2018 10:02:04 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-07-18"}
