m. As the global 21 cm measurements are\nrefined, the coupling redshift could change and we quantify how the FDM\nconstraint would be modified. A rough translation of the FDM mass bound to a\nthermal relic warm dark matter (WDM) mass bound is also provided.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 3 May 2018 12:25:25 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-07-18"}
