ts the program brings to its participants; the\nNITARP approach could be mirrored in similar professional development (PD)\nprograms in other STEM subjects.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 3 May 2018 15:57:49 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-06-20"}
